Yup, since the files for the play managers are all without versions (get stripped during module build) you don't ever know WHAT version of google-play.jar is the one being moved around.

Appcelerator now has at least 3 modules using google-play.jar.

The 'workaround' is NOT a viable mid/long term solution.
